name: Freedom
description: This video was made in solidarity with a Malaysian graphic artist Fahmi Reza who was arrested yesterday over his ‘Dengki ke?’ Spotify playlist .He has just been released today 24th April 2021 and now being investigated under the Sedition Act and Communications and Multimedia Act. This video was posted in different social medias and have received over 15000 viewers after a few hours it was posted on twitter.
